---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Rockstar Renovations.">
  <Navbar />
  <main>
    <header class="hero">
      <h1>Rockstar<br /><span>Renovations</span><br /><small>EST. 2020.</small></h1>
      <p>An fully insured business, both in general liability and workman’s compensation. Renovations for the modern style.</p>
      <a href="" role="button">Lets get Rocking</a>
    </header>

    <section class="divider">
      <div class="divider__line">&nbsp;</div>
      <small class="divider__text">WE GIVE THE ROCK STAR TREAMENT</small>
    </section>

    <section class="our-process">
      <header class="our-process__subtitle">
        <h2>Our process that rocks.</h2>
      </header>
      <article class="our-process__content">
        <ul>
          <li>1. Estimate</li>
          <li>2. Communicate</li>
          <li>3. Make it great</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="tiny-story">
      <p>Rockstar Renovations was started in January of 2020 as a side hustle for the owners, Michael and Brett. Soon, the two came to realize that their “side hustle” could be much more and they could even be their own bosses.</p>
      <a href="#" role="button">See Our Projects</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
